  assetTiers:
  - tierName: First Gold
    requiredAsset: 100
    milestoneText: "\"Congratulations! You can now afford a used e-bike\u2014at least
      you won't have to walk to your next deal.\""
  - tierName: Monthly Salary
    requiredAsset: 5000
    milestoneText: '"Equivalent to a white-collar worker''s monthly pay. Except you
      probably earned this in 5 seconds."'
  - tierName: Middle Class
    requiredAsset: 50000
    milestoneText: '"A year''s savings for a middle-class family. Or enough to buy
      loyalty from an entire Stone Age tribe."'
  - tierName: Luxury Entry
    requiredAsset: 300000
    milestoneText: "\"You can now buy a BMW 3 Series or Audi A4\u2014in cash. No
      financing needed.\""
  - tierName: Patek Philippe
    requiredAsset: 800000
    milestoneText: "\"Not just any watch\u2014a Patek Philippe Nautilus. Time is
      literally on your wrist now.\""
  - tierName: Yacht Life
    requiredAsset: 5000000
    milestoneText: '"5M Gold gets you a 35-foot pre-owned yacht. Don''t ask how far
      it can go. Ask where you''ll park it."'
  - tierName: Eight Figures
    requiredAsset: 10000000
    milestoneText: '"10 Million Gold! Remember when Wang Jianlin said ''set a small
      target of 100 million''? You''re 10% there. Well done."'
  - tierName: Gulfstream Ready
    requiredAsset: 50000000
    milestoneText: "\"Gulfstream G280\u2014a real business jet. Now you can do Stone
      Age deals in the morning and Tech Era deals by lunch.\""
  - tierName: Billionaire
    requiredAsset: 100000000
    milestoneText: '"One Billion Gold! Your wealth now rivals the GDP of a small
      country. Ever thought about running for office?"'
  - tierName: Elon Musk
    requiredAsset: 200000000
    milestoneText: "\"You've surpassed Elon Musk! You're no longer just the world's
      richest person\u2014you're the wealthiest being across all timelines.\""
